{
  "video_id": "9VWvF7dGed8",
  "title": "CREEPYPASTA | \"Bus Accident\" | Crypt TV Extended Universe",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 470.0,
      "end_time": 2200.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] The following\nis a catalog of events"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2200.0,
      "end_time": 5243.0,
      "text": "that occurred over the course\nof two weeks in the year 2011."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6130.0,
      "end_time": 8270.0,
      "text": "These strange and unnerving\nhappenings took place"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8270.0,
      "end_time": 12210.0,
      "text": "in Greene County, Illinois, a\nrural, sparsely-populated area"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12210.0,
      "end_time": 14760.0,
      "text": "located on the southwestern\npart of the state."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 14760.0,
      "end_time": 16900.0,
      "text": "The incidents have yet to be explained."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 16900.0,
      "end_time": 19990.0,
      "text": "Many theories have circulated\nas to what may have ensued,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 19990.0,
      "end_time": 21890.0,
      "text": "but at the time of this writing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 21890.0,
      "end_time": 24140.0,
      "text": "nothing has been corroborated."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24140.0,
      "end_time": 27293.0,
      "text": "The events in question are\npresented in chronological order."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28180.0,
      "end_time": 30866.0,
      "text": "Feel free to draw your own conclusions."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 30866.0,
      "end_time": 32750.0,
      "text": "(somber music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 32750.0,
      "end_time": 36133.0,
      "text": "Monday, February 28th, 2:10 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38340.0,
      "end_time": 40470.0,
      "text": "The accident is the\nbiggest anyone in the area"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40470.0,
      "end_time": 42243.0,
      "text": "has seen in 27 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43610.0,
      "end_time": 46800.0,
      "text": "A school bus full of Greenfield\nElementary third graders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46800.0,
      "end_time": 49370.0,
      "text": "on its way back from a\nfield trip to a local farm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 49370.0,
      "end_time": 51620.0,
      "text": "collides with a dump\ntruck and loses control."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 52810.0,
      "end_time": 55870.0,
      "text": "After impact, its wheels\nskid off the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 55870.0,
      "end_time": 57530.0,
      "text": "That's when momentum takes over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 57530.0,
      "end_time": 59910.0,
      "text": "causing it to roll three\ntimes before coming to a stop"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59910.0,
      "end_time": 62340.0,
      "text": "upside down in an irrigation ditch."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 62340.0,
      "end_time": 65020.0,
      "text": "Six children and one teacher are killed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 65019.99999999999,
      "end_time": 66450.0,
      "text": "14 others are injured."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 66450.0,
      "end_time": 68720.0,
      "text": "When police arrive on the\nscene, alcohol is detected"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 68720.0,
      "end_time": 71860.0,
      "text": "on the breath of the dump\ntruck driver, Ray Peck."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 71860.0,
      "end_time": 75040.0,
      "text": "He is arrested on site and\nbooked at the local jail"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 75040.0,
      "end_time": 76240.0,
      "text": "in Carrollton, Illinois."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 77940.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "Wednesday, March 2nd."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 83160.0,
      "text": "The only hotel in\nCarrollton, the Cat's Inn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 83160.0,
      "end_time": 84850.0,
      "text": "is booked to capacity."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 84850.0,
      "end_time": 86970.0,
      "text": "Family and friends begin\narriving in the town"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 86970.0,
      "end_time": 89550.0,
      "text": "to attend funerals and memorial services."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 89550.0,
      "end_time": 92333.0,
      "text": "A brown van is spotted in\nthe parking lot of the Inn."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 93280.0,
      "end_time": 96290.0,
      "text": "Thursday, March 3rd, 10:00 A.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 96290.0,
      "end_time": 98590.0,
      "text": "The funeral of Lily\nNorth, one of the girls"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98590.0,
      "end_time": 101490.0,
      "text": "who died in the accident,\noccurs on this morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101490.0,
      "end_time": 104440.0,
      "text": "Lily's mother Candace does not attend."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 104440.0,
      "end_time": 107440.0,
      "text": "Her husband, Jared, tells those who ask"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 108300.0,
      "end_time": 111263.0,
      "text": "that she's taken Lily's death very hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 112460.0,
      "end_time": 115463.0,
      "text": "Thursday, March 3rd, 2:00 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 116350.0,
      "end_time": 118230.0,
      "text": "A funeral for David Frost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118230.0,
      "end_time": 121060.0,
      "text": "another casualty of the accident, happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 121060.0,
      "end_time": 123940.0,
      "text": "It is a small service,\nonly intimate friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 123940.0,
      "end_time": 125620.0,
      "text": "of the family are invited."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 125620.0,
      "end_time": 128880.0,
      "text": "Alan Spencer, David's\nschoolmate and closest friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 128880.0,
      "end_time": 131390.0,
      "text": "is said to look the worse\nfor wear at the event,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 131390.0,
      "end_time": 133163.0,
      "text": "even more so than the Frost family."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 135620.0,
      "end_time": 138210.0,
      "text": "Spencer was in the bus during the accident"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 138210.0,
      "end_time": 140770.0,
      "text": "and even though he was\nsitting next to David,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 140770.0,
      "end_time": 144370.0,
      "text": "he managed to escape with only\na few bumps and scratches."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 144370.0,
      "end_time": 147810.0,
      "text": "However, the tragedy has\ntaken a psychological toll"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 147810.0,
      "end_time": 149520.0,
      "text": "on the young boy."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 149520.0,
      "end_time": 152110.0,
      "text": "He has complained of\nnightmares as of late."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 152110.0,
      "end_time": 155330.0,
      "text": "In these dreams, he mentions\nseeing his friend David,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 155330.0,
      "end_time": 158160.0,
      "text": "head dangling from a loose, broken neck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 158160.0,
      "end_time": 160660.0,
      "text": "walking into his bedroom and\nwhispering horrible things"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 160660.0,
      "end_time": 162370.0,
      "text": "to him in the night."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 162370.0,
      "end_time": 164410.0,
      "text": "His parents have begun\ndiscussing taking him"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 164410.0,
      "end_time": 167110.0,
      "text": "to a child psychologist\nin order to help him cope"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 167110.0,
      "end_time": 170220.0,
      "text": "with his guilt and grief\nsurrounding this accident."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 170220.0,
      "end_time": 171980.0,
      "text": "(somber music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 171980.0,
      "end_time": 174620.0,
      "text": "Thursday, March 3rd, 4:00 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 174620.0,
      "end_time": 177090.0,
      "text": "Mourners set up a road-side\nmemorial at the spot"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 177090.0,
      "end_time": 179860.0,
      "text": "where the accident occurred\nas a way to commemorate those"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 179860.0,
      "end_time": 181990.0,
      "text": "who had tragically lost their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 181990.0,
      "end_time": 185500.0,
      "text": "About seven people visit the\nsite between 4:00 and 7:00 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 185500.0,
      "end_time": 189660.0,
      "text": "The mourners park their cars\nalong the side of the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 189660.0,
      "end_time": 191483.0,
      "text": "A brown van is seen amongst them."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 192530.0,
      "end_time": 194790.0,
      "text": "There are songs and prayers."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 194790.0,
      "end_time": 197760.0,
      "text": "Flowers, teddy bears\nand hand-written letters"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 197760.0,
      "end_time": 200340.0,
      "text": "are placed at the spot of the accident."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 200340.0,
      "end_time": 201233.0,
      "text": "Candles are lit."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 202610.0,
      "end_time": 205573.0,
      "text": "It is said to be a beautiful memorial."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 207530.0,
      "end_time": 210593.0,
      "text": "Friday, March 4th, 11:00 A.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 212700.0,
      "end_time": 215540.0,
      "text": "John Mayhew, the teacher who\nwas killed in the accident,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 215540.0,
      "end_time": 218483.0,
      "text": "is cremated, there is no service."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 219320.0,
      "end_time": 222240.0,
      "text": "Lisa Mayhew, John's wife, takes the urn"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 222240.0,
      "end_time": 225263.0,
      "text": "containing her husband's\nashes back home with her."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 227600.0,
      "end_time": 229853.0,
      "text": "Friday, March 4th, 6:00 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 230920.0,
      "end_time": 232590.0,
      "text": "The first death is reported that evening"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 232590.0,
      "end_time": 234750.0,
      "text": "when Jared North returns\nhome from the grocery store"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 234750.0,
      "end_time": 237223.0,
      "text": "to find his wife, Candice, dead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 240930.0,
      "text": "the top half of her skull\nremoved with near-surgical"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 240930.0,
      "end_time": 244190.0,
      "text": "precision, her scalp\nis nowhere to be found."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 244190.0,
      "end_time": 246740.0,
      "text": "In her hand, she is clenching\nher daughter's brush."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 247980.0,
      "end_time": 250470.0,
      "text": "Police find no sign of forced entry"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 250470.0,
      "end_time": 252880.0,
      "text": "and hardly any evidence of scuffle."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 252880.0,
      "end_time": 255740.0,
      "text": "A full investigation into\nthe death of Candace North"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 255740.0,
      "end_time": 256573.0,
      "text": "is launched."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 258420.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261320.00000000003,
      "text": "On the brush, Jared would\nlater tell the papers..."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 262640.0,
      "end_time": 264840.0,
      "text": "- [Jared] She was holding Lily's brush,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 264840.0,
      "end_time": 266660.0,
      "text": "it meant a lot to her."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 266660.0,
      "end_time": 269210.0,
      "text": "Every night she would brush\nLily's hair before bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 270830.0,
      "end_time": 272530.0,
      "text": "I used to joke that Candace treated her"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 272530.0,
      "end_time": 275013.0,
      "text": "like one of those American\nGirl dolls, you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 278270.0,
      "end_time": 279370.0,
      "text": "Now they're both gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 282030.0,
      "end_time": 285300.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Saturday,\nMarch 5th, 3:00 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 285300.0,
      "end_time": 287180.0,
      "text": "A memorial service is\nheld on the football field"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 287180.0,
      "end_time": 289330.0,
      "text": "of North Greene High\nSchool that is attended"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 221968.0,
      "end_time": 223866.0,
      "text": "by over 700 people,\nincluding friends and family"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 223866.0,
      "end_time": 226114.0,
      "text": "of the deceased who had\ncome in from out of town."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 295800.0,
      "end_time": 297940.0,
      "text": "News of Candace North's murder"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 297940.0,
      "end_time": 299840.0,
      "text": "begins to spread throughout the event."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 301060.0,
      "end_time": 304403.0,
      "text": "Sunday, March 6th, 10:10 A.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 305370.0,
      "end_time": 307740.0,
      "text": "Alan Spencer's parents\nbring him to church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 307740.0,
      "end_time": 309770.0,
      "text": "but rather than forcing\nhim to attend the service"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 309770.0,
      "end_time": 312090.0,
      "text": "where the accident would be discussed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 312090.0,
      "end_time": 315570.0,
      "text": "they let him use the playground\nat the park next door."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 315570.0,
      "end_time": 318560.0,
      "text": "He is last seen climbing\na tree at 10:30 A.M.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 318560.0,
      "end_time": 320900.0,
      "text": "when Janet Finch cuts\nthrough the parking lot"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 320900.0,
      "end_time": 322250.0,
      "text": "on her way into the church."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 323230.0,
      "end_time": 326610.0,
      "text": "15 minutes later, the\ncongregation hears the scream"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 326610.0,
      "end_time": 329630.0,
      "text": "of Margaret Peters, who\nhad been walking her dog"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 329630.0,
      "end_time": 330673.0,
      "text": "down the sidewalk."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 331530.0,
      "end_time": 334200.0,
      "text": "The churchgoers empty into\nthe street and find Alan"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "lying on the ground, his head\ntwisted a full 180 degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 341570.0,
      "end_time": 344600.0,
      "text": "At the time it is believed\nAlan had fallen from the tree"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 344600.0,
      "end_time": 347993.0,
      "text": "and landed face first onto the\nasphalt, snapping his neck."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 350050.0,
      "end_time": 353710.0,
      "text": "Investigators on the scene\nfound a note in his back pocket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 353710.0,
      "end_time": 357723.0,
      "text": "it reads: \"If you yourself cannot release,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 359027.0,
      "end_time": 361867.0,
      "text": "\"then it will come to take a piece.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 364330.0,
      "end_time": 366840.0,
      "text": "Alan Spencer's parents\nlater confirm that the note"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 366840.0,
      "end_time": 369083.0,
      "text": "is not written in his handwriting."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 372260.0,
      "end_time": 375613.0,
      "text": "Sunday, March 6th, 3:34 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 377060.0,
      "end_time": 379250.0,
      "text": "Examiners discover that\naside from a broken neck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 379250.0,
      "end_time": 381900.0,
      "text": "Alan Spencer's corpse\nis missing four incisors"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 381900.0,
      "end_time": 383683.0,
      "text": "and two molars from his mouth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 385570.0,
      "end_time": 387020.0,
      "text": "none of which were recovered."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 387930.0,
      "end_time": 391100.0,
      "text": "Strangely enough, his\ninjuries mirror those"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 391100.0,
      "end_time": 393360.0,
      "text": "of his good friend, David Frost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 393360.0,
      "end_time": 395123.0,
      "text": "right down to the missing teeth."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 397070.0,
      "end_time": 400820.0,
      "text": "Monday, March 7th, 11:19 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 400820.0,
      "end_time": 403120.0,
      "text": "Cartoonist Dan Colb's Chevy Tahoe"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 403120.0,
      "end_time": 404450.0,
      "text": "is found on the side of the road"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 404450.0,
      "end_time": 407030.0,
      "text": "after running head first\ninto a telephone pole."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 407030.0,
      "end_time": 409900.0,
      "text": "When paramedics arrive, they\ndiscover him unconscious"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 409900.0,
      "end_time": 411703.0,
      "text": "in the driver's seat but breathing."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 412760.0,
      "end_time": 415070.0,
      "text": "Colb doesn't have any relation to anyone"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 415070.0,
      "end_time": 417400.0,
      "text": "who died in the bus accident on the 28th"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 417400.0,
      "end_time": 420633.0,
      "text": "but his wife passed on from\nbreast cancer two years prior."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 421500.0,
      "end_time": 424470.0,
      "text": "The widower, who lives alone\nin Carrollton, has attended"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 424470.0,
      "end_time": 427280.0,
      "text": "therapy twice a week since\nthe death of his wife."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 427280.0,
      "end_time": 429510.0,
      "text": "And those close to him later\nclaim that he never took off"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 429510.0,
      "end_time": 430360.0,
      "text": "his wedding band."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 431200.0,
      "end_time": 433440.0,
      "text": "His injuries include a separated shoulder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 433440.0,
      "end_time": 437720.0,
      "text": "a head contusion and a missing finger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 437720.0,
      "end_time": 441453.0,
      "text": "specifically the ring\nfinger of his left hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 442410.0,
      "end_time": 444723.0,
      "text": "His wedding band is also missing."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 445799.0,
      "end_time": 447570.0,
      "text": "He was taken to Saint Mary's General"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 447570.0,
      "end_time": 449063.0,
      "text": "and treated for his injuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 450290.0,
      "end_time": 454350.0,
      "text": "Tuesday, March 8th, 2:45 A.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 454350.0,
      "end_time": 455810.0,
      "text": "Neighbors report screaming coming from"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 455810.0,
      "end_time": 457060.0,
      "text": "the house of Lisa Mayhew."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 457930.0,
      "end_time": 460600.0,
      "text": "Police arrive to the home\nto find Mayhew in shock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 460600.0,
      "end_time": 462670.0,
      "text": "her speech is erratic and incoherent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 462670.0,
      "end_time": 464300.0,
      "text": "she is trembling uncontrollably"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 464300.0,
      "end_time": 466930.0,
      "text": "and she has an injury,\ndeep cuts on her left arm"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 466930.0,
      "end_time": 469130.0,
      "text": "that appear to have\nbeen left by an animal."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 469130.0,
      "end_time": 471640.0,
      "text": "Mayhew is given a sedative and treated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 471640.0,
      "end_time": 473950.0,
      "text": "but she does not answer\nany questions when asked"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 473950.0,
      "end_time": 476100.0,
      "text": "about where her injuries came from."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 476100.0,
      "end_time": 477950.0,
      "text": "Police notice the urn that once contained"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 477950.0,
      "end_time": 481570.0,
      "text": "her husband's ashes in\nthe bathroom, it is empty."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 481570.0,
      "end_time": 483010.0,
      "text": "And it appears, by the look of things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 483010.0,
      "end_time": 484910.0,
      "text": "that she flushed them down the toilet."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 486290.0,
      "end_time": 489430.0,
      "text": "Police find no evidence of\nforced entry into her home"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 489430.0,
      "end_time": 492080.0,
      "text": "but don't estimate the\npossibility of a break in"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 492080.0,
      "end_time": 493863.0,
      "text": "due to her bizarre babblings."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 494720.0,
      "end_time": 496370.0,
      "text": "Some of the things she is quoted in saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 496370.0,
      "end_time": 498070.0,
      "text": "are outlined in the police report."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 500030.0,
      "end_time": 502730.0,
      "text": "- [Lisa] I had to forget him\nor it would've killed me."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 503940.0,
      "end_time": 505333.0,
      "text": "Its mouth was so wide."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 506320.0,
      "end_time": 507613.0,
      "text": "So many teeth."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 509040.0,
      "end_time": 509873.0,
      "text": "Its face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 511159.0,
      "end_time": 513893.0,
      "text": "a face like patches of skin."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 515299.99999999994,
      "end_time": 517123.99999999994,
      "text": "John's gone now."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 517124.0,
      "end_time": 518126.0,
      "text": "(tape recorder clicking)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 518126.0,
      "end_time": 520130.0,
      "text": "(somber music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 520130.0,
      "end_time": 522510.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Lisa is taken\nto Saint Mary's where she's"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 522510.0,
      "end_time": 525160.0,
      "text": "treated for her injuries\nand kept under surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 526480.0,
      "end_time": 529600.0,
      "text": "But police call her sister,\nAva, who lives in Chicago"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 529600.0,
      "end_time": 531950.0,
      "text": "and inform her of the situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 531950.0,
      "end_time": 534879.0,
      "text": "She agrees to catch a flight\ndown the following day."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 534879.0,
      "end_time": 536530.0,
      "text": "(somber music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 536530.0,
      "end_time": 539930.0,
      "text": "Tuesday, March 8th, 3:35 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 539930.0,
      "end_time": 541910.0,
      "text": "Dan Colb awakes in the hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 541910.0,
      "end_time": 544923.0,
      "text": "he is lucid but unresponsive to questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 545900.0,
      "end_time": 548550.0,
      "text": "In fact, he refuses to speak at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 548550.0,
      "end_time": 550580.0,
      "text": "Doctors decide to keep\nhim for an extra day"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 550580.0,
      "end_time": 553280.0,
      "text": "to monitor him for brain\ntrauma before releasing him."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 553280.0,
      "end_time": 555530.0,
      "text": "A nurse, Margo Johnson, gives him a pencil"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 555530.0,
      "end_time": 557570.0,
      "text": "and a pad of paper in\ncase he might want to"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 557570.0,
      "end_time": 560573.0,
      "text": "write down his thoughts since\nhe doesn't wish to talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 563020.0,
      "end_time": 566563.0,
      "text": "Wednesday, March 9th, 8:55 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 567560.0,
      "end_time": 570280.0,
      "text": "Police find Ray Peck dead in his cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 570280.0,
      "end_time": 571580.0,
      "text": "he's been horribly maimed."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 574630.0,
      "end_time": 578230.0,
      "text": "There was a hole in his\nside the size of a softball."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 578230.0,
      "end_time": 580270.0,
      "text": "It was later discovered\nthat his liver was removed"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 580270.0,
      "end_time": 583520.0,
      "text": "and taken by whoever had\ncommitted the heinous murder."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 583520.0,
      "end_time": 587177.0,
      "text": "On the wall, written in Peck's\nown blood, is the phrase,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 587177.0,
      "end_time": 589597.0,
      "text": "\"If you yourself cannot release,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 589597.0,
      "end_time": 592380.0,
      "text": "\"then it will come to take a piece.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 592380.0,
      "end_time": 594530.0,
      "text": "Police have no leads on\nwho snuck into Peck's cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 594530.0,
      "end_time": 595380.0,
      "text": "and murdered him."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 596270.0,
      "end_time": 598370.0,
      "text": "The security footage is of little use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 598370.0,
      "end_time": 600480.0,
      "text": "the camera pointed at\nhis cell cuts to black"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 600480.0,
      "end_time": 604280.0,
      "text": "roughly between the times\nof 8:40 and 8:43 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 604280.0,
      "end_time": 605680.0,
      "text": "It is believed that the murder occurred"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 605680.0,
      "end_time": 607350.0,
      "text": "during these three minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 607350.0,
      "end_time": 610200.0,
      "text": "but the speed in which it\nmust've happened is astounding."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 611070.0,
      "end_time": 613350.0,
      "text": "None of the other security\ncameras at the jail"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 613350.0,
      "end_time": 615163.0,
      "text": "show anything out of the ordinary."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 616130.0,
      "end_time": 619300.0,
      "text": "Given the note found in his\nback pocket, with a phrase"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 619300.0,
      "end_time": 622180.0,
      "text": "matching the one written\non the wall of Peck's cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 622180.0,
      "end_time": 624060.0,
      "text": "a murder investigation is now opened up"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 624060.0,
      "end_time": 625683.0,
      "text": "into Alan Spencer's death."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 627000.0,
      "end_time": 630913.0,
      "text": "Thursday, March 10th, 10:05 A.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 632170.0,
      "end_time": 635340.0,
      "text": "Nurse Margaret Johnson enters\nDan Colb's hospital room"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 635340.0,
      "end_time": 637060.0,
      "text": "to find that he is missing."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 637060.0,
      "end_time": 639590.0,
      "text": "It appears, at some\npoint during the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 639590.0,
      "end_time": 642140.0,
      "text": "he changed into his clothes\nand exited the hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 642140.0,
      "end_time": 644070.0,
      "text": "without anyone noticing."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 644070.0,
      "end_time": 645830.0,
      "text": "She finds the notebook that she gave him"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 645830.0,
      "end_time": 646973.0,
      "text": "had been left behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 648050.0,
      "end_time": 649813.0,
      "text": "Johnson would later tell reporters."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 651680.0,
      "end_time": 652990.0,
      "text": "- [Margaret] There were\nthese weird pictures"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 652990.0,
      "end_time": 654270.0,
      "text": "that he had drawn in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 654270.0,
      "end_time": 656550.0,
      "text": "The man, or thing, I don't know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 656550.0,
      "end_time": 659240.0,
      "text": "it wore a suit but it had like a big,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 659240.0,
      "end_time": 661880.0,
      "text": "wide smile and these sharp teeth."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 661880.0,
      "end_time": 664450.0,
      "text": "The drawings were really good but they"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 664450.0,
      "end_time": 665770.0,
      "text": "gave me the creeps."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 665770.0,
      "end_time": 668190.0,
      "text": "And that smile was all\nthere was to its face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 668190.0,
      "end_time": 669920.0,
      "text": "the rest of the thing's\nface was nonexistent."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 669920.0,
      "end_time": 672750.0,
      "text": "He must've drawn it over a dozen times."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 672750.0,
      "end_time": 676052.0,
      "text": "There were also pictures\nof a pocket watch with"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 676052.0,
      "end_time": 678690.0,
      "text": "like a kind of eye on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 678690.0,
      "end_time": 682180.0,
      "text": "To tell you the truth, for\nsome reason I can't explain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 682180.0,
      "end_time": 684733.0,
      "text": "that bothered me more than the man thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 685699.0,
      "end_time": 687070.0,
      "text": "(tape recorder clicking)"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 687070.0,
      "end_time": 689650.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] The only words\nthat Colb had managed to write"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 689650.0,
      "end_time": 694137.0,
      "text": "was the familiar phrase, \"If\nyou yourself cannot release,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 694137.0,
      "end_time": 696217.0,
      "text": "\"then it will come to take a piece.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 697520.0,
      "end_time": 700490.0,
      "text": "Colb would not be seen\nagain for three months."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 700490.0,
      "end_time": 703610.0,
      "text": "It is not known what he\nwas doing during this time."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 703610.0,
      "end_time": 706390.0,
      "text": "Margaret reported Colb's\ndisappearance to the hospital staff"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 706390.0,
      "end_time": 708510.0,
      "text": "and left the notebook on the counter."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 708510.0,
      "end_time": 710500.0,
      "text": "It would sit there for four\nhours until it was picked up"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 710500.0,
      "end_time": 712860.0,
      "text": "by Lisa Mayhew while she\nwas being checked out"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 712860.0,
      "end_time": 714950.0,
      "text": "of Saint Mary's by her sister, Ava."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 714950.0,
      "end_time": 717560.0,
      "text": "When Lisa saw the\nillustrations Colb had drawn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 717560.0,
      "end_time": 719280.0,
      "text": "they triggered a panic attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 719280.0,
      "end_time": 722040.0,
      "text": "She screamed and began to throw\na fit in the hospital lobby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 722040.0,
      "end_time": 725010.0,
      "text": "only calming down after\nbeing given a sedative."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 725010.0,
      "end_time": 726380.0,
      "text": "Lisa would travel to Chicago"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 726380.0,
      "end_time": 728602.0,
      "text": "with her sister later that evening"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 728602.0,
      "end_time": 731002.0,
      "text": "and would never set foot\nin Greene County again."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 732490.0,
      "end_time": 735770.0,
      "text": "Over the next four months,\nshe would sell her home"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 735770.0,
      "end_time": 739300.0,
      "text": "then go back to her maiden name, Fitzroy."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 739300.0,
      "end_time": 743260.0,
      "text": "To this day, she has refused\nto answer any emails or calls"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 743260.0,
      "end_time": 746770.0,
      "text": "regarding her husband,\nthe accident, her injuries"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 746770.0,
      "end_time": 750348.0,
      "text": "or what happened the night\npolice were called to her home."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 750348.0,
      "end_time": 753090.0,
      "text": "(somber music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 753090.0,
      "end_time": 755373.0,
      "text": "Friday, March 11th, 4:00 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 756840.0,
      "end_time": 759200.0,
      "text": "Police issue a statement\nthat they believe Donnelson"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 759200.0,
      "end_time": 761940.0,
      "text": "was responsible for the deaths\nof at least three people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 761940.0,
      "end_time": 765510.0,
      "text": "Candace North, Alan Spencer and Ray Peck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 765510.0,
      "end_time": 767810.0,
      "text": "but that investigation is\nongoing until they deduce"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 767810.0,
      "end_time": 769700.0,
      "text": "how the murders were committed."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 769700.0,
      "end_time": 772130.0,
      "text": "The cryptic phrase found on the Donnelson"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 772130.0,
      "end_time": 773960.0,
      "text": "hotel room is the piece of evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 773960.0,
      "end_time": 776043.0,
      "text": "that makes Donnelson the prime suspect."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 777940.0,
      "end_time": 779490.0,
      "text": "Saturday, March 12th, 6:00 A.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 780350.0,
      "end_time": 782600.0,
      "text": "The Greene County Gazette\npublishes the Sheriff's statement"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 782600.0,
      "end_time": 785893.0,
      "text": "regarding Donnelson, papers\nare distributed country wide."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 787720.0,
      "end_time": 790670.0,
      "text": "Saturday, March 12th, 2:00 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 790670.0,
      "end_time": 793020.0,
      "text": "Police are called to the\nspot where the February 28th"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 793020.0,
      "end_time": 795210.0,
      "text": "school bus accident\noccurred by Bell Parker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 795210.0,
      "end_time": 797383.0,
      "text": "a teacher at the Greenfield Elementary."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 799180.0,
      "end_time": 802080.0,
      "text": "She shows them something\nstrange that she's discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 802080.0,
      "end_time": 805560.0,
      "text": "at the memorial, a ring of\ncandles that had been set up"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 805560.0,
      "end_time": 808550.0,
      "text": "on the side of the road, a\nnote that had been slipped"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 808550.0,
      "end_time": 810180.0,
      "text": "under one of the candles."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 810180.0,
      "end_time": 813040.0,
      "text": "She had found it while paying\nher respects to the deceased,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 813040.0,
      "end_time": 816210.0,
      "text": "then dialed 911 when she\nrecognized that it had"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 816210.0,
      "end_time": 819897.0,
      "text": "the same thing that had\nbeen reported in the papers."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 819897.0,
      "end_time": 822427.0,
      "text": "\"If you yourself cannot release,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 822427.0,
      "end_time": 824307.0,
      "text": "\"then it will come to take a piece.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 826020.0,
      "end_time": 829190.0,
      "text": "Saturday, March 12th, 3:30 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 829190.0,
      "end_time": 831810.0,
      "text": "Margaret Johnson delivers the pad of paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 831810.0,
      "end_time": 834320.0,
      "text": "with Don Colb's drawings\nto the Sheriff's station,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 834320.0,
      "end_time": 836380.0,
      "text": "pointing out that he had\nwritten dozens of times"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 836380.0,
      "end_time": 838680.0,
      "text": "the same cryptic message that had appeared"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 838680.0,
      "end_time": 840430.0,
      "text": "at the other crime scenes."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 840430.0,
      "end_time": 842300.0,
      "text": "Colb becomes a person of interest"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 842300.0,
      "end_time": 845050.0,
      "text": "and when it is discovered that\nhe has seemingly left town,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 845050.0,
      "end_time": 848060.0,
      "text": "an APB is put out for his arrest."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 848060.0,
      "end_time": 851793.0,
      "text": "Sunday, June 12th, 10:00 P.M."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 853580.0,
      "end_time": 857510.0,
      "text": "Dan Colb is killed on\nInterstate 65 in Huntsville,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 857510.0,
      "end_time": 859700.0,
      "text": "Alabama when he stepped out in the road"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 859700.0,
      "end_time": 861453.0,
      "text": "in front of a speeding semi truck."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 862927.0,
      "end_time": 864620.0,
      "text": "The driver told police\nthat he didn't see him"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 864620.0,
      "end_time": 865723.0,
      "text": "until it was too late."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 867510.0,
      "end_time": 869610.0,
      "text": "He would say to reporters..."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 869610.0,
      "end_time": 872200.0,
      "text": "- [Truck Driver] The only thing\nI saw was a big, wide smile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 872200.0,
      "end_time": 874320.0,
      "text": "then a second later, I heard the thud"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 874320.0,
      "end_time": 875620.0,
      "text": "and I knew that I hit him."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 877490.0,
      "end_time": 880420.0,
      "text": "His face wasn't right,\nhis eyes were massive."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 880420.0,
      "end_time": 882830.0,
      "text": "I know I only saw him\nfor a second but I swear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 882830.0,
      "end_time": 885350.0,
      "text": "I could tell something\nweren't right in him."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 885350.0,
      "end_time": 886183.0,
      "text": "Like there was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 887080.0,
      "end_time": 888670.0,
      "text": "like there was some kind of sickness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 888670.0,
      "end_time": 890197.0,
      "text": "pain behind them and he,"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 892230.0,
      "end_time": 893223.0,
      "text": "and he was happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 895160.0,
      "end_time": 896660.0,
      "text": "Happy it was all about to end."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 898827.0,
      "end_time": 899660.0,
      "text": "(tape recorder clicking)"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 899660.0,
      "end_time": 901863.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] In the glove\ncompartment of Colb's car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 902750.0,
      "end_time": 904820.0,
      "text": "police found a notebook\nwith dozens of illustrations"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 904820.0,
      "end_time": 907820.0,
      "text": "of the same creature that he\nhad drawn in the hospital room."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 909100.0,
      "end_time": 912840.0,
      "text": "On nearly every page, the art\nwas accompanied by the same"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 912840.0,
      "end_time": 916123.0,
      "text": "cryptic phrase that haunted\nGreene County investigators."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 918557.0,
      "end_time": 920783.0,
      "text": "\"If you yourself cannot release,"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 922037.0,
      "end_time": 925717.0,
      "text": "\"then it will come to take a piece.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 927787.0,
      "end_time": 930454.0,
      "text": "(ominous music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 932920.0,
      "end_time": 935020.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] Watch new,\nscary vids every Tuesday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 935020.0,
      "end_time": 936607.0,
      "text": "Thursday and Friday."
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 936607.0,
      "end_time": 940024.0,
      "text": "(heavy electronic music)"
    }
  ]
}